<h2>1. Purpose</h2>
<p><strong>TGB Channels (Official AI)</strong> is an internal automation system built and operated by SoleBlessing Ventures Corporation. It automates scheduling and publishing of approved content‚Äîsuch as photos, videos, and reels‚Äîon <strong>The Gold Blessing</strong> official Facebook Page using Meta‚Äôs Graph API.</p>
<p>This tool is accessible only to verified administrators and is not available for public use.</p>

<h2>2. Information We Access</h2>
<p>The app retrieves limited technical data via Meta‚Äôs Graph API:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Facebook Page ID and Access Token (to authorize posting)</li>
  <li>Post metadata such as IDs, permalinks, likes, shares, and view counts</li>
</ul>
<p>No customer or follower personal data is collected, stored, or processed.</p>

<h2>3. How We Use This Information</h2>
<p>Information is used exclusively to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Publish official content to The Gold Blessing Facebook Page</li>
  <li>Refresh tokens and retrieve analytics</li>
</ul>
<p>All processing occurs within secure Meta and Google Workspace environments.</p>

<h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>All access tokens and logs are stored within <strong>Google Apps Script</strong> and <strong>Google Sheets</strong>, accessible only by authorized admins. No third-party service outside Meta or Google receives this data. SoleBlessing follows Google Workspace and Meta API security standards.</p>

<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share data with any external parties.  
Meta Platforms Inc. and Google LLC process data independently under their own privacy policies.</p>

<h2>6. Rights and Removal</h2>
<p>Admins who wish to revoke access may:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Remove the <strong>TGB Channels (Official AI)</strong> app from Facebook Business Integrations, or</li>
  <li>Email <a href="mailto:inquiry@soleblessing.com">inquiry@soleblessing.com</a> to request complete deletion of data.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Updates to This Policy</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to comply with new requirements. The revised version will be posted here with a new ‚ÄúLast Updated‚Äù date.</p>

